setdefaultpenx 8
setdefaultpeny 40
resetpage

 SetAPen grey220
  print Press
 setapen cyan240
  print  Space
 SetAPen grey220
  print  at any time to remove the newest layer of hilited cells.
showpage
waitmouseorkey
resetpage
